description: I. NHS dental statistics for England. Quarter 2: 30 September 2008. 53 p. II. Table showing the number of patients receiving NHS dental teatment in England for each year from 31/03/2006 to 30/09/2008, broken down by Strategic Health Authority and Primary Care Trust, with separate statistics for children and for adults, for CoTs, for treatment band, and for patients as a percentage of the population. 99 p.
